Book.create(title: "Berserk", isbn: "0-4749-8285-8", year: "1989", price: 19.99, buy: "9.3/10", image: "https://thebiem.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/berserk.jpg.webp", description: "Berserk mainly centers around Guts’ character, born from his mother’s corpse, who becomes a mercenary because he doesn’t know anything else he could do. He spends his life on the battlefield, fighting because he doesn’t know any better. The Band of the Hawk, under the tutelage of their leader, Griffith, takes Guts in. The manga then chronicles his journey with the troop as he tries to make his way up the ranks and combines greed for power with the desperation to discover his true purpose in life.", author_id: a5.id)
Book.create(title: "One Piece", isbn: "0-8488-8307-1", year: "1996", price: 15.99, buy: "10/10", image: "https://thebiem.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/One-Piece.jpg.webp", description: "Monkey D. Luffy is a young man who sets out on an adventure on the East Blue Sea to find the famed treasure One Piece. He believes that finding it will make him the King of Pirates. He befriends several companions on the way, including a thief, a sniper, a womanizer, an assassin, and lots more. With his effortlessly cheerful attitude and ship, the Going Merry, Luffy will stop at nothing to defeat what may come and find his treasure.", author_id: a1.id)
Book.create(title: "Vagabond", isbn: "0-1789-5431-4", year: "1980", price: 20, buy: "8/10", image: "https://thebiem.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/vagabond.jpg.webp", description: "Shinmen Takezou is a young man with an aggressive demeanor who decides to leave his village with his best friend to find a greater purpose in life. Together, the two enlist in the Toyotomi army. But after their crushing defeat, the two-part ways, and Takezou realizes that he’s a wanted man back home. A priest gives him a new name to make his escape and lead a better life: Musashi Miyamoto.", author_id: a2.id)
Book.create(title: "Kingdom", isbn: "0-4924-9558-0", year: "", price: 20, buy: "8.7/10", image: "https://thebiem.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/kingdom.jpg.webp", description: "Xin and Piao, two war-orphans who live in Qin’s kingdom in war-torn China and dream of becoming Great Generals in the warring forces. However, Piao is suddenly taken away from Xin and returns months later on the verge of death. To discover what happened to his friend, Xin discovers that Piao served as an identical-looking body double for Ying Zheng, the Qin empire’s current king. Xin uses it as his chance to not only avenge his friend’s death but also fulfill his dream of becoming the greatest general of all time.", author_id: a3.id)
Book.create(title: "Slam Dunk", isbn: "0-4949-0766-5", year: "", price: 20, buy: "7/10", image: "https://thebiem.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Slam-Dunk.jpg.webp", description: "Hanamichi Sakuragi is a delinquent who often gets the ladies running…away from him, that is. Until he meets Haruko Akagi, the girl of his dreams, who introduces him to the school basketball team. Initially reluctant, Sakuragi joins the team and is a natural at the sport. Together with other misfits, the team starts pulling its weight to take out the national championship.", author_id: a4.id)
Book.create(title: "Vinland Saga", isbn: "321", year: "", price: 20, buy: "9/10", image: "https://thebiem.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Vinland-Saga.jpg.webp", description: "Set in the era of the Vikings, Thorfinn is the son of one of the greatest warriors. As eager as he is, he sneaks on to the ship of his father to get fighting experience. This little act of his ultimately causes his father to die for Thorfinn’s sake. He challenges Askeladd to a duel and fails as he is not skilled enough yet. With a thirst for vengeance, Thorfinn spends his childhood with the crew that killed his father, slowly honing his skills for battle. One day, however, Askeladd receives notice that Canute, a Danish prince, has been taken hostage. Askeladd takes this as an opportunity to hatch a plan that will change the lives of everyone.", author_id: a3.id)
Book.create(title: "One Punch Man", isbn: "321", year: "", price: 20, buy: "10/10", image: "https://thebiem.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/One-Punch-Man.jpg.webp", description: "Saitama is a hero who started because he loved the experience of it. However, he trained himself so much that by now, he’s able to defeat almost any foe with a single punch. But he doesn’t get any recognition for his enormous strength. He quickly gets bored of this immense power and loses interest in heroics. He meets a few people along the way, including the cyborg Genos, who encourages him to join the Hero Association. Even there, though, his incredible power is unrecognized, and he’s just living out a boring, ultra-powerful existence.", author_id: a3.id)
Book.create(title: "Death Note", isbn: "321", year: "", price: 20, buy: "10/10", image: "https://thebiem.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/death-note.jpg.webp", description: "Light Yagami mysteriously finds the ‘death note’ in a notebook, which allows the user to kill anyone as long as they remember their name and face. Light decides to use it to create a utopian world free of crime. Ryuk, the God of death and the death note’s original owner, decides to help Light. Together, they set out to create a crime-free world while also contending with those investigating the mysterious spate of deaths taking place worldwide.", author_id: a3.id)
Book.create(title: "Hunter x Hunter", isbn: "321", year: "", price: 20, buy: "10/10", image: "https://thebiem.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/hunter-x-hunter.jpg.webp", description: "Gon Freecss believes that both his parents are dead. However, he eventually finds out his father is still alive and is a prolific Hunter, someone who carries out explorations and hunts wrongdoers. Gon decides to leave home and take the Hunter exam himself, to become a Hunter and find his father, possibly bringing him back home. On his way, he meets several other aspirants who set out on a collective quest to rise to the elite rank of Hunter extraordinaire.", author_id: a3.id)
Book.create(title: "Nana", isbn: "321", year: "", price: 20, buy: "7/10", image: "https://thebiem.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Nana.jpg.webp", description: "The series gets its name from its two main characters – Nana Komatsu and Nana Osaki. Komatsu is a young girl in love who follows her friends and boyfriend to Tokyo to live a great romance. On the other hand, Osaki is a punk-rock singer who makes her way to Tokyo to start her music career. The two meet on the train there by chance, and again at an apartment they both find. They decide to become roommates and eventually become close friends and confidantes as they both look for what they want the most – love and fame.", author_id: a3.id)
Book.create(title: "Rurouni Kenshin", isbn: "321", year: "", price: 20, buy: "6/10", image: "https://thebiem.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/rurouni-kenshin.jpg.webp", description: "Himura Kenshin is a peacekeeper in Japan’s Meiji era, going around with his reverse blade sword and offering assistance to people who need it. He’s atoning for his actions in the Bakumatsu war, where he was a brutal assassin known as Hitokiri Battosai. He meets Kamiya Kaoru, who runs a dojo for swordsmanship, and decides to stay with her and her students while facing new and old enemies and trying to live up to his promise not to kill anyone anymore.", author_id: a3.id)
Book.create(title: "Hajime No Ippo", isbn: "321", year: "", price: 20, buy: "8.2/10", image: "https://thebiem.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/hajime-no-ippo.jpg.webp", description: "Ippo Makunouchi is a shy and timid boy who is often picked on. After one particularly savage beating, a professional boxer named Mamoru Takamura saves Ippo and takes care of him at the nearby gym. Ippo takes out his frustrations on a sandbag, and seeing his impressive skill, Takamura acknowledges that he could be a great boxer. And Ippo begins his training at the gym to become the Japanese and, sooner or later, World Champion.", author_id: a3.id)
Book.create(title: "Dorohedoro", isbn: "0-4924-9558-0", year: "", price: 20, buy: "7.2/10", image: "https://thebiem.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/dorohedoro.jpg.webp", description: "‘Hole’ is a dark district where death is commonplace for the weak at magic users’ hands. Magic users treat people in the Hole as nothing more than filthy insects. But these magic-users stand at a much higher status and prey on the weak by using them in their experiments. As a result, the powerless dwellers of the Hole make regular visits to the hospitals. Kaiman, a man with the face of a reptile, was one such individual. But instead of sitting back, he hunts the magic users with the help of his immunity to their powers. On his quest to restore his life and identity, Dorehedoro refreshingly combines comedy and death.", author_id: a3.id)
Book.create(title: "Tokyo Ghoul", isbn: "321", year: "", price: 20, buy: "8.6/10", image: "https://thebiem.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/tokyo-ghoul.jpg.webp", description: "College student Ken Kaneki’s date almost kills him when she turns out to be a ghoul, a human flesh-devouring supernatural being. After undergoing surgery, Ken becomes a half-ghoul and needs to feed on human flesh to survive. A ghoul family takes him in and teaches him how to discreetly living, being a ghoul while keeping his identity secret from his human companions, and avoiding the ghoul-hunting organizations.", author_id: a3.id)
Book.create(title: "Ouran High School Host Club", isbn: "0-4924-9558-0", year: "", price: 20, buy: "7/10", image: "https://thebiem.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/ouran-high-school-host-club.jpg.webp", description: "Haruhi is a bright young student who secures a prestigious spot at Ouran High School where only the richest of the rich play. She stumbles on to the Host Club, a group of pretty boys who spend their time pleasing the girls at the academy. After breaking a costly vase of theirs, Haruhi becomes their errand boy. ‘Boy’ because she looks masculine, is generally pleasing to the ladies, and they’ve just assumed she is one. Now Haruhi, an absolute commoner, needs to mix in with the Host Club playboys’ extravagant lives without arousing suspicion.", author_id: a3.id)
Book.create(title: "Black Butler", isbn: "321", year: "", price: 20, buy: "6/10", image: "https://thebiem.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/black-butler.jpg.webp", description: "Ciel Phantomhive is a thirteen-year-old detective called ‘the Queen’s watchdog’ in the Victorian Era. His position came after his parents were killed, and a group of attackers tortured him. He eventually comes into contact with a demon, who agrees to help Ciel with his plan for revenge in exchange for his soul. The demon takes on the guise of a butler named Sebastian Michaelis and helps Ciel with his daily investigations.", author_id: a3.id)
Book.create(title: "Attack on Titan", isbn: "0-4924-9558-0", year: "", price: 20, buy: "8.9/10", image: "https://thebiem.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/attack-on-titan.jpg.webp", description: "Attack on Titan is Eren Yeager’s story, a young boy who witnesses the destruction of his hometown and the brutal death of his mother at the hands of colossal humanoid creatures called ‘Titans.’ The Titans have managed to breach the walls that humanity built to ensure their safety. And they’re back in stronger numbers to fulfill their taste for human flesh. Eren decides to join the Survey Corps to defeat the Titans himself and help his friend Armin and adoptive sister, Mikasa.", author_id: a3.id)
Book.create(title: "Dragon Ball", isbn: "321", year: "", price: 20, buy: "", image: "https://thebiem.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/dragon-ball.jpg.webp", description: "Dragon Ball revolves around Son Goku, a young boy who may sometimes look like a monkey but is one of the most powerful warriors in the land. And he doesn’t even know it! He’s on a search for the seven legendary dragon balls which will summon a wish-granting dragon. On his way, he trains, meets several people, picks up a few allies along the way, and even strikes up a few fights. But even the most powerful foes can’t stand up to Goku, a child flying on a cloud.", author_id: a3.id)
Book.create(title: "Fruits Basket", isbn: "0-4924-9558-0", year: "", price: 20, buy: "", image: "https://thebiem.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/fruits-basket.jpg.webp", description: "Tohru Honda is orphaned when her mother dies in a car crash. With no place to go apart from her uncomfortable grandfather’s, she stays with popular kid Yuki Soma and his family. But she stumbles upon a Soma family secret – they’ve been cursed to turn into the animals of their Chinese zodiac sign under certain conditions. Tohru decides to keep their secret and encourages them to come out of their shell while also finding a cure for their curse.", author_id: a3.id)
Book.create(title: "Doraemon", isbn: "321", year: "", price: 20, buy: "", image: "https://thebiem.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/doraemon.jpg.webp", description: "Doraemon arrives from the 22nd century to aid Nobita Nobi, a child with horrible grades, a lazy attitude, and a frequent bully’s target. Nobita’s descendants believe that having the gadget-wielding Doraemon by his side would improve Nobita’s life and, therefore, their own. Nobita is smart enough to take good advantage of Doraemon, who stores a seemingly infinitesimal amount of gadgets in his little pocket for any situation.", author_id: a3.id)
Book.create(title: "Fullmetal Alchemist", isbn: "0-4924-9558-0", year: "", price: 20, buy: "", image: "https://thebiem.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Fullmetal-Alchemist.jpg.webp", description: "Fullmetal Alchemist is a story of two brothers, Edward and Alphonse, who decide to attempt human transmutation: the one forbidden act of Alchemy. As the law of Alchemy states, to obtain something, something of equal value must be lost. This results in Edward losing his left leg and right arm and Alphonse his complete physical body, replacing them with cybernetic ‘automail’ and integrating his soul into that of a suit of armor, respectively. The two then set about on a pursuit for the mystical Philosopher’s Stone that could potentially reverse the effects and put them back in their original bodies while simultaneously getting caught up in the political intrigue of their nation.", author_id: a3.id)
Book.create(title: "Gintama", isbn: "321", year: "", price: 20, buy: "", image: "https://thebiem.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/gintama.jpg.webp", description: "Gintoki Sakata is a former samurai who lives in feudal Japan that has been overtaken by the Amanto race of aliens. Not knowing how to do much else, he starts the ‘prestigious’ organization of Yorozuya. He performs odd jobs for a small fee so that he can buy his favorite milkshakes. And also perhaps helping him retreat to a time when he was useful. That is when he isn’t on the run from the police, the aliens, or a bunch of other people he’s wronged.", author_id: a3.id)
Book.create(title: "Cardcaptor Sakura", isbn: "0-4924-9558-0", year: "", price: 20, buy: "", image: "https://thebiem.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/cardcaptor-sakura.jpg.webp", description: "10-year-old Sakura Kinomoto accidentally releases a set of cards sealed in her basement called Clow Cards descended from an ancient sorcerer. The guardian of the cards, Cerberus, tasks her with retrieving them all. Sakura then sets out to find all the cards again, with her best friend and battle outfit designer Tomoyo and her older brother Toya while battling the cards’ magical personifications.", author_id: a3.id)
Book.create(title: "Blade of the Immortal", isbn: "321", year: "", price: 20, buy: "", image: "https://thebiem.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Blade-of-the-Immortal-640x852.jpg.webp", description: "Manji has gained an infamous name as the ‘Hundred Man Killer,’ on account of killing a hundred innocent men. However, this swordsman has something even more frightening up his sleeve. He’s immortal. An old nun named Yaobikuni placed bloodworms in his body to heal any wound in Manji’s body. Yaobikuni states that she will undo the curse of immortality if he kills one thousand evil men. After this ordeal, Manji runs into Rin Asano, a teenager with a troubled past. Due to her lack of strength, Manji agrees to protect her for four years. Once this partnership is set, the two go on a journey filled with vengeance, redemption, and bloodshed.", author_id: a3.id)
Book.create(title: "The Rose of Versaille", isbn: "0-4924-9558-0", year: "", price: 20, buy: "", image: "https://thebiem.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/the-rose-of-versailles.jpg.webp", description: "This manga revolves around two central characters, the first being the French Royal Guard named Oscar. Except, Oscar’s a woman who’s father raised her like a man because, sadly enough, she didn’t even want a daughter. Oscar is principled and noble, never stopping in her aim to do as much good as she can for her country, even if it means leaving a few broken hearts along her way. This brings us to our second lead, the Queen of France, Marie Antoinette. Antoinette is beautiful and knows it. However, she’s confined by royalties’ responsibilities and doesn’t get to live out her own dreams and fantasies.", author_id: a3.id)
Book.create(title: "To Your Eternity", isbn: "321", year: "", price: 20, buy: "", image: "https://thebiem.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/To-Your-Eternity.jpg.webp", description: "A mysterious, immortal being named ‘It’ was sent to the Earth. It has no emotions or identity. However, we know that It possesses a unique power – taking the shape of dying things with a strong ‘impetus.’ It transforms from a sphere to a rock and then moss. One after another, It takes the shape of those with a stronger impetus than the last. Finally, It takes the form of a boy living in the middle of a ghost town. Now a boy, It departs on an endless journey of new people, places, and experiences.", author_id: a3.id)
Book.create(title: "Black Jack", isbn: "321", year: "", price: 20, buy: "", image: "https://thebiem.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/blackjack.jpg.webp", description: "The mysterious doctor known as Black Jack is an enigma in the medical world. No one quite knows where he came from, and he doesn’t even have a license. But no one can deny that he is a genius, able to treat almost any medical ailment and go to great lengths to do so. If you can pay the very, very exorbitant price that comes with it, that is. With his assistant Pinoko, Black Jack aims to rid the world of the disease forever while working in the shadows.", author_id: a3.id)
Book.create(title: "Hana-Kimi", isbn: "321", year: "", price: 20, buy: "", image: "https://thebiem.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/hana-kimi.jpg.webp", description: "Mizuki Ashiya, a Japanese girl, living in the United States, sees a high jumper, Izumi Sano, on TV and instantly falls for him. So she decides to attend Osaka High School to win him over. However, since it’s an all-boys school, she has to go in the guise of a male. She finally meets Izumi, along with all the other boys in her own and the adjoining dormitories that make up the eclectic and multicultural mix of Osaka High School.", author_id: a3.id)
Book.create(title: "Claymore", isbn: "0-4924-9558-0", year: "", price: 20, buy: "", image: "https://thebiem.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/claymore.jpg.webp", description: "Raki is a young boy whose village is attacked by Yoma, humanoid human-flesh-eating demons with shape-shift. Clare is a Claymore, female half-human half-Yoma warriors assigned to protect the people for a fee, saving Raki. With Raki’s family dead, he starts following Clare on her journey as she searches for personal revenge on her Yoma past and discovers more dark secrets about the Claymore initiative.", author_id: a3.id)
Book.create(title: "Case Closed", isbn: "0-4924-9558-0", year: "", price: 20, buy: "", image: "https://thebiem.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/case-closed.jpg.webp", description: "Jimmy Kudo was a high school detective, quite popular and very good at his job, even helping out the police on occasion. A case leads him to be captured by the Black Organisation, who feed him a poison that turns him into a small kid. Jimmy adopts Conan’s identity and lives with his childhood friend Rachel and her father Richard, a private detective himself. He also enrolls himself in elementary school and forms a Junior Detective club, solving cases with them and Richard.", author_id: a3.id)